com.launchdarkly.client

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.launchdarkly.client.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    A User object contains specific attributes of a user browsing your site. The primary property is their key, which must uniquely identify each user. For authenticated users, this may be a username or e-mail address. For anonymous users, this could be an IP address or session ID.
